# Hello Notion Frontend

- Use hello-notion-fe and vercel-react-best-practices. Prefer Server Components; minimal props across server/client boundary.
- Structure: app/ for routes, components/ for UI, lib/ for API and auth helpers.
- Auth UI integrates with Supabase Auth. Keep accessibility and responsive layout.
